無痛死法<br />\n安樂死貌似都會窒息一段時間<br />\n只能靠快狠準<br />\n<br />\n我呢啲冇膽匪類只可以每日諗住想死然後繼續過日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:41:28.000Z","msg":"安樂死係訓著死 應該好舒服"},{"pid":"584b62a9c36a884e3d6cbec051830a12e3fedb4c","tid":2114833,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b71371d3e4ac2fad401b045aef751b32d9386b","tid":2114833,"uid":53396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0159982b81eaf1c791459a70cc771f4028091db6","tid":2114833,"uid":948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2e051b6a50e806ed365aa8104664751df4c5f3","tid":2114833,"uid":53396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"死係解決唔到問題<br />\n死前先諗一諗身邊總有一個係唔想見到你死就可以<br />\n你死係好易可以好快<br />\n但留低嘅問題要由身邊尚在世嘅人受返<br />\n又何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n停一停，想一想"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"嗰種情緒嚟嗰陣會稔<br />\n點解全世界都咁幸福<br />\n得自己過成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喊想死嗰陣某種程度係想解脫之餘<br />\n亦想令身邊嘅人都好似我咁唔開心就好<br />\n<br />\n所以係唔會咁理性稔得咁正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲道理相信每個情緒病嘅人都知<br />\n但當下嘅痛苦真係太難受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補充返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已走出陰霾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"人比人比死人<br />\n正等於三浦先生呢單嘢咁我哋表面睇佢好幸福好成功人生贏家咁<br />\n點解尋日突然就爆咁大單嘢出嚟嚇親全日本甚至亞洲地區fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又代入返你個故事，可能你睇全世界都好幸福<br />\n但世上比你更慘嘅人多到真係1人用口水都浸得死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最起碼你仲可以上連登可以食3餐<br />\n世上好多人唔好講食3餐，可能就嚟餓死<br />\n唔開心，每個人都有<br />\n但我哋身處香港，我相信香港人都有好多人真係有愛去對人<br />\n身邊總有人可以值得一齊去傾訴吐苦<br />\n連登都唔係程日個個都發膠post又係咁嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時傾下d苦況，總有巴打絲打會明會一切圍爐盡訴心中情"},{"pid":"8c492802bd2401b1502639bd6f56682dc86ea5a6","tid":2114833,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:45:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbA2PMx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbA2PMx.gif&h=0b33dd26&s={SIZE}\" />願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"9b7eb99945c99b3ee353bb061b9d766563947ce8","tid":2114833,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係一種無形嘅心理病嚟"},{"pid":"41bd4a26728cef82a40b627937dffa1d01e14e4b","tid":2114833,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3cc04c190fa49c018deb16ad8c0f72a497b12b9","tid":2114833,"uid":201601,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"三浦春馬係比你x死㗎喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7acfc97c1de561a4698c4ab62e9b759dd2a912","tid":2114833,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"以前青春期無拖拍時 每日有一個時間會同自己講好想扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n久而久之十年後都仲係毒撚"},{"pid":"0e0bde95a83633f3dd8aa8d6fe25609d080ccc50","tid":2114833,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41bd4a26728cef82a40b627937dffa1d01e14e4b","tid":2114833,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3cc04c190fa49c018deb16ad8c0f72a497b12b9","tid":2114833,"uid":201601,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"三浦春馬係比你x死㗎喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"係你爆父哥出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538dd3dba8d3ee197e315cd951f0fe69a9bc8e79","tid":2114833,"uid":81140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"之前有幾年，但同friends一次爆哂出嚟，有即刻好到，開始有改善。但係都要好長時間先真係好啲"},{"pid":"a43aa9c2962adbb2ec525624ef5bca642cac1b0e","tid":2114833,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ab5dee413eb4831a556ba9ff326f61112d36bc","tid":2114833,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"583eb27b3e7776face2f9e0ce5676c27c4c28e23","tid":2114833,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:53:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edfdda3e6bc37a0341b5f4b4bfe61974c9f1fcb2","tid":2114833,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1510f417a99f60ef70032ed1a9a5a5c1e75f3527","tid":2114833,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"生存係呢個荒謬既世界裡面，自殺其實是一種十分合理的決定，我地不必鼓勵自殺，但也不應把它當成絕對的惡"},{"pid":"8fd7b240c7980b74796d6782dd74b02b23d1368a","tid":2114833,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1510f417a99f60ef70032ed1a9a5a5c1e75f3527","tid":2114833,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"生存係呢個荒謬既世界裡面，自殺其實是一種十分合理的決定，我地不必鼓勵自殺，但也不應把它當成絕對的惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"安樂死萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d72e63d0630235200cc19584682bf27c4a3b63b","tid":2114833,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2e051b6a50e806ed365aa8104664751df4c5f3","tid":